About this item

  • Cricket Kit Bag for storing and carrying around cricket gear and other essentials
  • Made using water-resistant polyester fabric on the outside and polyester fabric on the inside
  • High-quality zipper tested for 500 cycles for smooth opening and closing mechanism
  • Has undergone 19 product tests to ensure sturdiness and durability
  • Provision of a side compartment to specifically accommodate a long cricket bat
  • Consists of one compartment on the front and side each for smaller items such as mobile and keys
  • Comprises ample space to carry two sets of racquets, padded gloves, leg guards, helmet, cricket balls, extra pair of clothes, shoes, water bottle, fitness accessories such as bands, grips, and more
  • Adjustable straps allow you to carry it on the back without any hassle
  • Product Dimensions: 76 x 35 x 23 cm (29.92 x 13.78 x 9.05 inches); Weight: 1230 grams
  • Package Contents: Amazon Brand - Solimo Cricket Kit Bag; Colour: Black

What is in the box?

  • Basics

    • From the manufacturer

    High-quality composition

    The exterior of the bag is manufactured using water-repellent polyester fabric, while the inside is made using polyester fabric. This makes the bag sturdy and durable.

    Spacious bag

    It consists of one compartment on the front and one on the side for smaller items such as mobile and keys. It has ample space for two sets of racquets, padded gloves, leg guards, a helmet, cricket balls, extra pair of clothes, shoes, a water bottle, fitness accessories such as bands, grips, and more.

    Tested for quality

    It is equipped with a high-quality zipper that is tested for 500 cycles. Additionally, the badminton kit bag has undergone 19 product-related tests.

    Premium Quality. Great Value.

    Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do.
